  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Childcare Support at Disaster-Stricken Tohoku</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In tsunami-stricken Rikuzen Takada City, many children lost family members, and exhibit psychological problems and very rough behavior. Especially pronouced is a case of lost mother with unemployed father inexperienced in child rearing. A childcare-support NPO, Kirarin (Shining) Kids needs professional training and skill-level improvement to cope with this unusually difficult situation. DSIA is trying to help financing the training of Kirarin Kids, so that it can serve a wider disaster area.</narrative>
  </description>
